replies.body:
It sounds like those permissions were able to get you started patching, but now we're running into some kind of weird connection issue...
{{sticker:zombie-brand-clap}} 

No worries though! Since you're able to get up to 99% sometimes, it probably just means that the download is having some hiccup and it can't finish. Hit up this [**connection guide**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/201752664-Troubleshooting-Connection-Issues) and let me know if that gets you back on the Rift!

Well, I tried everything on the connection guide and the issue still persisted. The client now consistently reaches 75% only for the percentage to slowly drop down every minute or so. Still shows the same error though. 
FeelsBadMan
{{sticker:zombie-nunu-bummed}}
